Description: Neutral Evade turns to mist, granting Nightshade 5% base damage as Lifesteal for 5s. Perfect Dodge doubles duration.

Name: Prismatic Driver
Description: Fires a superheated beam which deals 25 Mod Damage per second. Sustaining the beam on a target causes an explosion which deals 150 Mod damage in a 3m AOE.

Name: Blaze | Smolder
Description: Charge Melee Attacks apply BURNING which deals 150 FIRE damage over 5s

Name: Blood Draw
Description: Shoots out razor-sharp Chain Shards which impale up to 5 targets within 15m, dealing 10 damage. On hit, chains are pulled towards the caster, dealing 250 damage split equally among enemies and applying 275 BLEEDING damage over 15s.

Name: Bloodline | Merciless
Description: Fires a devastating blast which penetrates through all enemies in its path. Deals 120 damage with a 25% Critical damage bonus, and 2x additional stagger. Bloodline damage increases by 50% for each enemy penetrated.

Name: Bloodthirst | Assassin's Dagger
Description: Damage increases by +25% against BLEEDING enemies, and +25% when attacking from behind. Charge Attacks deal 100 BLEEDING damage over 10s

Name: Chaos Driver | Enigma
Description: Drives electrified rods which tether to other rods within 10m. Tethers deal 20 SHOCK damage per second. Targets embedded with a rod take 20 SHOCK damage per second. They take 20% additionally damage per extra rod in the target. Damage is increased by 1.5% if linked to another rod. Rods in the same target will not link.

Name: Concussive Blast
Description: Fires a focused blast of air through all targets within 8m, dealing 155 damage and 5x impact.

Name: Corrosive Rounds
Description: Imbues ammunition with TOXIC and increases Range Crit Chance by 15% for 20s. Shots also apply CORRODED, dealing 100 damage over 10s.

Name: Cube Shield | Cube Gun
Description: Generates a Cube Shield which absorbs up to 500 damage from incoming enemy projectiles. Lasts 15s. Reactivating fires the Cube Shield which damages enemies as is travels. Damage is increased if the Cube Shield has absorbed enemy projectile damage before firing.

Name: Death Sentence | Feral Judgement
Description: Dealing Melee Damage 6 times over 10s empowers Feral Judgement. When empowered, Neutral Backdash Charge Attacks apply Death Sentence. After 1.5s of being sentenced, the enemy will suffer 10 Phantom Strikes, dealing X25 Damage each. Deals 25% additional damage to BLEEDING enemies.

Name: Defrag
Description: Infects weapon with Malware for 30s, causing shots to apply FRAGMENTED for 5s. When a FRAGMENTED enemy dies, they create a Glitch that lasts 15s. Picking up a Glitch increases All damage by 20% for 15s. Destroying a Glitch causes it to destabilize, creating a 5m Virus Pool which deals 25 damage per second and applies the FRAGMENTED debuff to enemies inside. Virus Pools last 15s.

Name: Dreadwalker | Nightfall
Description: Enter the Nightmare Realm. Nightfall gains infinite Ammo, a 25% Fire Rate increase, 10% Lifesteal, and becomes fully automatic. The wielder becomes significatly harder to hit while moving. Disables other weapons and Skills for the duration, or until Dreadwalker is deactivated. Lasts 10s.

Name: Dreamwave | Dreamcatcher
Description: After dealing 250 damage, Charge Attack will release a Dreamwave, flowing outwards 20m and returning to caster. Dreamwave applies SLOW to all enemies for 10s and grants a Stack of REVERIE for each enemy affected. Each Stack grants +2% to All Damage and +2% Movement Speed, which lasts 15s.

Name: Dying Breath | Gas Giant
Description: When infused, Neutral Backdash Charge Attack explodes in a 3m. AOE and leaves an ACID Cloud which last for 15s.

Name: Energy Wall
Description: Deploys an energy barrier on impact with ground. Allies can shoot through Energy Wall but enemy projectiles are absorbed (up to 500 damage received). Max 1 Wall at a time. Lasts 30s.

Name: Energy Wave | Hero's Sword
Description: Charge attacks use 35 stamina to release an energy wave projectile allowing the wielder to strike enemies from much farther away.

Name: Eulogy | Sorrow
Description: Recalls bots which deal 30 damage when pulled from a target and when striking targets on their return. Recalled bolts grant 2% of Max HP. Recalled bolts can also overfill Sorrow by up to +5. Any additional bolts will be returned to reserves.

Name: Explosive Shot | Hellfire
Description: Fires an explosive round that deals up to 155 damage within 9m.

Name: Familiar
Description: Summons Faerie Familiar to aid in combat. The Familiar selects a random enemy within 10m and slashes through them for 25 damage each attack. Familiar will select a new target when the previous one dies. Lasts 15s.

Name: Faultline | Stonebreaker
Description: Charge to fire off ground-based shockwaves which deal 115 damage. Costs 35 Stamina

Name: Firestorm
Description: Creates a whirling cyclone that sucks in nearby targets and applies BURNING for 10s. The center of the cyclone deals 75 FIRE damage per second. Lasts 15s.

Name: Fission Strike | Atom Splitter
Description: On Neutral Evade Attacks Atom Splitter achieves Nuclear Fission, releasing a wave of charged particles which deals 151.5 Damage to targets within 10m. Charged Neutral Evade Attacks increase range by 3x and Damage by 25%

Name: Gravity Core | Starkiller
Description: Fires a highly compressed sphere which draws in objects and deals 50 damage on impact. When colliding with a target, a large Gravity Well opens and draws in objects for 5s. When the Gravity Well expires, it deals 250 damage within 10m. Adds 200 damage per enemy and divides total damage among all enemies.

Name: Guardian's Call | Twisted Arbalest
Description: Calls down a Guardian Sword on enemies struck by an Energy Disc. Swords deal 100 damage and 3x stagger within 5m.

Name: Healing Shot
Description: Launches a payload that explodes on contact with allies, healing 30% of their max health. When no ally is struck, payload lays dormant until an ally gets close. Dormant payload lasts 30s, slowly losing healing potency over time.

Name: Heat Sink | Plasma Cutter
Description: Forces open Plasma Cutter's heat vents dispersing all heat. While active, Plasma Cutter generates 50% less heat, and ramping damage cap is increased to 3x Damage. Overheats automatically when deactivated. Lasts 20s.

Name: Helix
Description: Shoots a helix of missiles, dealing 120 damage. On contact, divides into 6 smaller rockets which seek additional targets, dealing 30 damage on contact.

Name: Horizon Strike | World's Edge
Description: Charge Attacks release a wide horizontal projectile that penetrates through multiple enemies dealing 116 damage.

Name: Hot Shot
Description: Imbues ammunition with FIRE and increases Ranged damage by 15% for 20s. Shots also apply BURNING, dealing 200 FIRE Damage over 10 seconds.

Name: Krell Edge | Krell Axe
Description: Charge to throw the Krell Axe which applies OVERLOAD on hit, dealing 50 SHOCK Damage every 5s for 10s. Shortly after throwing, another will appear in the wielders hand. Costs 25 Stamina

Name: Lifeline | Red Doe Staff
Description: After dealing 250 damage, the next charge attack causes the spirit of the RED DOE to stampede forward, dealing 160 damage to enemies and regenerating 10% Health to allies in its path.

Name: Moonlight Barrage | Crescent Moon
Description: Empowers the Bow for 15s. Arrows apply Moonlight to enemies for 3s. Enemies struck by Crescent Moon while Moonlit release a Moon Essence which returns 1 arrow, heals 5% of Max Health, and grants 15% Fire and Reload Speed for 5s. Basic Shots automatically become Charged Shots. Manually Charged Shots fire two arrows.

Name: Nano Swarm | Nebula
Description: Unleash a swarm of Nanomachines that seek after enemies within 20 meters and repeatedly attack dealing 6 ACID damage per hit. Lasts 15 seconds

Name: Ouroboros | Deceit
Description: Conjures 3 sword fragments that encircle the wielder for 30s. Performing a Melee Attacks lets loose a Fragment which taints the blood of targets, causing all attacks from Deceit to register as Weaspot hits for a short period of time. Charge Melee attack fires all remaining Fragments at once.

Name: Overflow
Description: Imbues ammunition with SHOCK and increases Fire Rate by 15% and Reload Speed by 15% for 20 seconds. Shots also apply OVERLOADED, dealing 35 SHOCK Damage every 5s for 15s.

Name: Labyrinth Staff
Description: Basic Strikes generate 10% additional Mod Power. Charge Attacks perform an AOE which strikes all enemies within 2m, dealing 75 Damage. AOE Damage generates 50% additional Mod Power.

Name: Root Blades
Description: Fires a volley of Root Blades in an arc which each deal 25 Damage and apply 200 BLEEDING damage over 10s

Name: Rootlash
Description: Launches a projectile which summons a Root Tentacle. Tentacles deal 30 damage and steal 1.5% of the hero's Max Health per hit. Lasts 20s. (Max 2)

Name: Rotted Arrow
Description: Fires a rotten arrow that deals 20 damage and detonates for another 60 damage within 4m. A deadly gas cloud is left behind that deals 200 damage over 5s.

Name: Scrap Shot
Description: Fires a caltrops grenade that explodes to cover an area of 6m. Caltrops deal 20 damage per second and SLOW to enemies that walk over them. Lasts 10s.

Name: Screamer | Meridian
Description: Fire a high-powered rocket that deals up to 200 damage within 2.5m.

Name: Shatterstar | Savior
Description: Imbues shots with white hot FIRE. Hits apply BURNING, dealing 250 FIRE damage over 10 seconds. Lasts 20s. Weakspot Hits and Kills cause shots to fragment, automatically targeting nearby enemies. Fragments strike for 30% of the initial damage dealt and apply BURNING.

Name: Skewer
Description: Fires a Wretched Spear which embeds itself on contact. Spears deal 125 damage on hit, rapidly dividing inside the target until bursting, dealing 140 damage to all targets within 3m. Spears embedded in the environment remain in place for 10s.

Name: Song of Eafir
Description: Fires a shot infused with the binding power of the Song of Eafir. Staggers most ground enemies within 10m and deals 150 damage to Flying enemies within the same range. The song continues for 15s, afflicting targets within 15m with SLOW, and a 15% decrease to damage dealt.

Name: Soul Brand | Rune Pistol
Description: Applies a Soul Brand to all enemies within 25m which lasts 25s. Enemies killed while bearing the Soul Brand leave behind an Echo which lasts 10s before returning to the Nightmare Realm. Echoes are drawn to any survivor who walks within 3m, granting 10% of Max Health on contact.

Name: Soulbinder
Description: Fires a projectile that attaches to the enemy dealing 40 damage. Enemies within 7m become bound to the primary target after impact and share 60% of damage dealt to them. Lasts 15s.

Name: Space Crabs
Description: Launch an alien egg that bursts on impact, releasing 5 Space Crabs. Crabs follow the caster, leaping towards enemies within 4m, and exploding, dealing 60 Damage each.

Name: Sporeshot | Sporebloom
Description: Fires a rotten spore that explodes dealing 125 damage within 6m and leaves a deadly gas cloud that applies SLOW while dealing 15 damage per second for 7s.

Name: Starfall | Saggitarius
Description: Fires a powerful arrow which deals 30 damage and opens a 7m portal that rains down star fragments. Each fragment deals 50 damage within 4m. Lasts 6s.

Name: Stasis Beam
Description: Fires a beam which deals 15 damage per second, and applies SLOW Debuff. After 3s of application to a target, SLOW becomes STASIS, freezing the target in place for 10s.

Name: Supernova | Aphelion
Description: Fires the compressed remains of a dying star. On contact or hit wit the primary fire, causes Supernova to explode for 150 FIRE Damage, and 350 BURNING Damage over 10s to all targets within 4m. Striking the Supernova with Aphelion's primary fire increases its explosion radius by 25% and damage by 50%, and spawns a massive shockwave that deals 300 FIRE damage and also applies the initial BURNING amount.

Name: Time Lapse
Description: Creates a 6m blast which freezes all standard enemies for 7s. Dealing damage to frozen enemies immediately breaks the Time Lapse effect, applying SLOW for the remaining duration.

Name: Tremor
Description: Fires a projectile that cracks the ground and spawns shockwaves that deal 75 damage Within 9m for 6s. Shockwaves inflict 3x impact.

Name: Voltaic Rondure
Description: Launches a slow-moving orb that pulses every 0.5s, striking enemies within 3m for 20 SHOCK damage and applying OVERLOADED for 15s. The orb lasts 20s. The orb can be overcharged by striking it with additional damage.

Name: Whirlwind | Spectral Blade
Description: Neutral Backdash Charge creates a Whirlwind of slashes which strike all enemies within 8m for 75 damage.

Name: Witchfire
Description: Fires a highly volatile projectile that explodes to leave a line of flaming terrain. Deals 55 FIRE Damage per second, and applies BURNING, dealing 200 damage over 10s. Lasts 5s.

Name: Assassin's Dagger | Bloodthirst
Description: Lightweight. Silent. Deadly. It's rumored that the blade is meant to bestow a slow, agonizing death.

Name: Atom Smasher | Accelerator
Description: A powerful crushing device that harnesses rocket technology to increase smashing force.

Name: Atom Splitter | Fission Strike
Description: A giant tool for splitting heavy rocks.

Name: Blade of Adventure
Description: A long, sharp blade hammered out of vehicle leaf springs. Well-rounded for most situations.

Name: Blade of Gul
Description: A short, but thick sword, used by Gul Warriors. It's compact design makes for swift yet hard-hitting blows. An excellent close-range option.

Name: Bone Chopper
Description: A razor-sharp hand axe. Excellent for separating flesh from bone. Charge for double attacks.

Name: Decayed Claws
Description: Makeshift claws fashioned from decayed root and rusted metal.

Name: Dreamcatcher | Dreamwave
Description:
There is an ethereal lightness to this weapon, as though it were made of paper or breath.
Though it strikes its foes forcibly enough.

Name: Edge of the Forest
Description: An elegant, yet light blade, designed to bring beauty to bloodshed. Unstoppable in the hands of a master swordsman.

Name: Feral Judgement | Death Sentence
Description: A pair of gauntlets with sharp crystal blades that strike with vicious speed and velocity.

Name: Gas Giant | Dying Breath
Description: Dealing damage unleashes the dormant Toxic Gas within the head. When infused, Basic Attacks apply CORRODED for 5s.

Name: Hero's Sword | Energy Wave
Description: An ancient, quick, and versatile blade suited for many situations. Charge attacks cast a projectile for dealing melee damage at range.

Name: Huntress Spear | Athibar
Description: The spear is oddly...quiet. Even when you slide your hand across its haft or drop it upon the ground, it makes an unthinkably small amount of noise.

Name: Iron Greatsword
Description: A giant broadsword made from flattened railroad tracks. Dozens of ridges cut in the side for causing irreparable damage.

Name: Knuckle Dusters
Description: Steel knuckles with rusty sawblade tips, designed to boost Unarmed damage.

Name: Krell Axe | Krell Edge
Description: Infused with Krell Shock magic, can be thrown if the wielder has stamina. Axe will magically reappear in-hand. Charge to throw.

Name: Amplify | Archon
Description: Increases Mod Damage by +30% and grants +10% Mod Critical Chance.

Name: Nightshade | Beyond the Veil
Description: An ancient, quick, and versatile blade suited for many situations. Charge attacks cast a projectile for dealing melee damage at range.

Name: Ornate Blade
Description: An intricately-forged elongated sword. Designed to keep stronger enemies at bay, while remaining light enough for agile maneuvers.

Name: Ornate Flail
Description: An intricately-forged mace with uniquely designed airways. Allows smaller wielders to get the mace up to speed much quicker.

Name: Rebellion Spear
Description: A spear perfect for staying at a distance. Has excellent range, great recovery, and focused direct damage for one on one combat.

Name: Red Doe Staff | Lifeline
Description: A magical stave rumored to contain a healing spirit within. Strikes with wide swings.

Name: Royal Broadsword
Description: Standard issue Greatsword for the Empress's Royal Guards. Razor-sharp edges, extremely heavy, yet perfectly balanced.

Name: Rusted Claws
Description: A pair of old-canine training bracers converted into deadly claws. Used for slashing and ripping.

Name: Scrap Hammer
Description: A large, heavy warhammer cobbled together from engine components. It is a slow- but-devastating weapon meant to destroy anything it hits.

Name: Scrap Hatchet
Description: A common chopping tool that has been repurposed for combat. Rapidly cycles attacks from right to left. Charge attacks strike twice.

Name: Scrap Staff
Description: A staff made from old plumbing parts used for controlling wide swaths in front of the wielder.

Name: Smolder | Blaze
Description: A scorched blade imbued with FIRE.

Name: Spectral Blade | Whirlwind
Description: A super-heated laser sword with an infinitely sharp edge. Perfect for cutting... anything.

Name: Steel Flail
Description: An unorthodox weapon meant to convert momentum into destruction. Some attacks can continuously chain overhead swings.

Name: Steel Katana
Description: An old piece of steel with serrations cut into one side. Pipe handle provides limited grip.

Name: Steel Spear
Description: A spear perfect for staying at range with quick, focused attacks. High, single-target damage.

Name: Steel Sword
Description: A long, sharp blade hammered out of vehicle leaf springs. Well-rounded for most situations.

Name: Stonebreaker | Faultline
Description: A massive Greatsword which contains the harnessed magic of a corrupted Guardian. Can summon small shockwaves.

Name: Vice Grips
Description: A N'Erudian tool converted into a ruthless ripping device. High raw damage.

Name: World's Edge | Horizon Strike
Description:
A glowing Greatsword forged from shards of a shattered Worldstone. Charge
attacks cast waves.

Name: Dominator | Summoner
Description: Increases Mod and Skill Damage by 35% and Skill and Mod Critical Chance by 5% while a Minion is active. Sacrificing a Minion increases Ranged and Melee Damage by 30% and Ranged and Melee Critical Chance by 5% for 30s or until another Minion is summoned.

Name: Backbone | Medic
Description: Increases the hits Medic can take before losing Grey Health by 2.

Name: Benefactor | Medic
Description: Increases Relic Use Speed by 20%. Relic Use gains -1 Stagger.

Name: Benevolence | Medic
Description: Increases Relic Efficacy by 15% and heals nearby allies for 30% of the total healing value, increasing to 60% for any below 35% max health.

Name: Best Friend | Handler
Description: Using a Relic fully restores the Companion's health and grants them 25% Damage and 35% Damage Resistance for 15s.

Name: Bonded | Handler*
Description: When Handler is downed, Companion will attempt to revive them at 50% Max Health. Can be used to revive allies with Command. Downed ally must have a Relic charge.

Name: Circumvent | Invader
Description: Reduce Cost of Evade and Combat Slide by 15%. Perfect Dodges gain an additional 15% reduction

Name: Close Quarters | Challenger
Description: Grants a 35% increase to All Damage to enemies within 10m. Damage bonus tapers off until 20m. Critical Chance is increased by up to 10%

Name: Dead to Rights | Hunter*
Description: Dealing 55 Base Ranged Weakspot Damage extends the duration of active Hunter Skills by 3.5s. Can extend timer beyond its initial duration.

Name: Deadeye | Hunter
Description: Gain 40% Ranged Damage and 15% Weakspot Damage and 5% Ranged Critical Chance.

Name: Die Hard | Challenger*
Description: When receiving fatal damage, the Challenger becomes invulnerable for 3s and regenerates 100% of Max Health. Can only happen once every 10 minutes. Resets at Worldstone or on death.

Name: Power Creep | Archon
Description: After casting a Mod, 5% of the Mod Power spent will be regenerated by all allies over 10s. While Power Creep is active. allies will also gain 5% Mod Power Generation.

Name: Experimentalist | Alchemist
Description: Using a Relic applies a random buff on the Alchemist and allies within 20m for 60s. Cannot be overridden.

Name: Face of Danger | Challenger
Description: Using a Relic within 10m of an enemy grants 2 stacks of Bulwark and 10% Increased Damage for 10s.

Name: Gold to Lead | Alchemist
Description: Picking up Scrap or Metals also has a 15% chance to award Ammo to the Alchemist.

Name: Heavy Mobility | Engineer
Description: While Carrying a Heavy Weapon, Movement Speed is increased by 35% and both Evade Speed and Evade Distance are increased by 25%

Name: High Tech | Engineer*
Description: Overclock a Carried or Deployed Heavy Weapon. Overclocking grants infinite Ammo, increased Fire Rate, and a 25% damage increase for 25s

Name: Incite | Summoner
Description: Using a Relic grants Minions 5% Max HP per second, and increases their damage dealt by 15% and Crit Chance by 15%. Lasts 30s.

Name: Intimidating Presence | Challenger
Description: After activating a Challenger Skill, enemies within 15m deal 10% less damage for 15s, with an additional 2.5% damage reduction per enemy affected (Max 10%).

Name: Intuition | Hunter
Description: Using a Relic extends the duration of any active Hunter Skill by 10s. Effect degrades with each subsequent use. Weakspot Kills against MARKED enemies increase speed of next Relic Use within 15s by 5%. Stacks 10x.

Name: Invigorated | Medic
Description: Grants a 25% increase to All Damage and 5% Critical Chance.

Name: Liquid Courage | Alchemist
Description: Grants a 25% increase to All Damage and 5% Critical Chance.

Name: Loaded | Gunslinger*
Description: When activating any Gunslinger Skill, both weapons are instantly reloaded, and gain infinite reserve ammo on all weapons for 8s.

Name: Loophole | Invader
Description: All ally Ranged and Melee damage against enemies distracted by the Invader's Decoy grants 7.5% as Lifesteal.

Name: Lucky | Explorer*
Description: Grants a 35% chance to spawn additional items and rarer drops when defeating stronger enemies.

Name: Magnetic Field | Engineer
Description: Heavy Weapons grant 15% Damage Reduction and gradually restore Ammo to allies within 2.5m

Name: Metal Detector | Explorer
Description: Increase Ammo, Currency, and Metal Drop Rate Chance for entire party by 10%. Prospector increases the chance of Consumables being rewarded from Chests

Name: Metalworker | Engineer
Description: Increases Skill Damage by 50% and Skill Critical Chance by 10%. Heavy Weapons gain 50% Ammo Capacity, 25% Max Health, and 25% Weakspot Damage

Name: Outrage | Summoner
Description: Sacrifice grants 3% Lifesteal for each Minion Sacrificed, and increases Movement Speed by 15%. Lasts 10s.

Name: Override | Invader
Description: Using a Relic reduces Threat Generation by 25% for 10s. While Override is active, the next Evade leaves a Empowered Decoy which lasts 5.5s.

Name: Pack Hunter | Handler
Description: Gain 30% Ranged and Skill Damage and 5% Ranged and Skill Critical Chance while Companion is active and within 40m of the player.

Name: Panacea | Alchemist
Description: Curative effects apply to all allies within 15m and grant 15 additional Resistance. Allies affected by Panacea gain +10% Status and Blight Resistance.

Name: Posse Up | Gunslinger
Description: Ammo pickups award 30% additional Ammo per player with the bonus split equally among teammates. Causes Ammo Box to drop additional ammo on the ground.

Name: Power Leak | Archon
Description: Using a Relic grants 200 Mod Power for both equipped Mods. Grant an additional 100 Mod Power to the current mod.

Name: Spirit Within | Archon
Description: Reduces the Mod Power requirement for all Mods by 15%. After casting a Mod instantly regain 15% of the Mod Power spent.

Name: Powerlifter | Challenger
Description: Both the Stamina cost increase for each weight bracket and Stamina Regen Delay are reduced by 50%.

Name: Prospector | Explorer
Description: Relic Fragments discovered by Explorer drop at a higher quality. When picking up a gem, Explorer has a 5% chance of picking up a second one of the same type/quality.

Name: Quick Hands | Gunslinger
Description: Firearms gain 10% Reload Speed. Bonus is DOUBLED if magazine is empty

Name: Regenerator | Medic*
Description: After restoring 250 Total Health to allies, regain a spent Relic charge. Resting or Respawning at a Worldstone resets healing accumulation. Each additional player increases the healing requirement by 50%.

Name: Residue | Summoner
Description: Minions that expire leave a 3m Aura which heals 2.5% Health per second and increases Healing by 20%. Lasts 10s.

Name: Return to Sender | Hunter
Description: Kills due to Weakspot and Critical Hits increase Ammo drops by 50% and double the chance of Ammo drops.

Name: Ruthless | Summoner*
Description: When the Summoner deals damage to their Minion, it causes them to ENRAGE. Minions gain 50% increased Damage, Attack Speed, and Movement Speed. Lasts 40s.

Name: S.H.A.R.K. | Invader
Description: Sprinting for 1s or Evading adds 1 Stack of Momentum which increases Ranged and Melee damage by 7% and Ranged and Melee Critical Chance by 1% for 15s. Max 5 Stacks.

Name: Scavenger | Explorer
Description: Pickups increase All Damage Dealt by 5% per stack for 20s. Additional Stacks increase Duration, up to 60s. Max 5 Stacks | Scavenger also increase All Crit Chance by 5% while active.

Name: Self Discovery | Explorer
Description: After using a Relic, Scavenger gains 6 total stacks and prevents Stack Decay for 30s.

Name: Shadow | Invader*
Description: Casting an Invader Skill leaves a Decoy for 3s which draws enemy fire. Deal +15% additional damage to enemies not targeting Invader.

Name: Sleight of Hand | Gunslinger
Description: Using a Relic reloads equipped Firearm and increases Ranged Damage by 15% for 10s.

Name: Spirit of the Wolf | Handler
Description: Increases Movement Speed by 10%. All allies within 10m of the Handler gain the Handler's Movement Speed (if faster). Reduces the Stamina Cost of actions for allies by 15%.

Name: Tempest | Archon*
Description: Automatically generate 3 Mod Power per second. Casting a Mod increases all Mod Generation by 100% for 10s.

Name: Spirited | Alchemist*
Description: Alchemist can have 3 additional Concoction buffs active.

Name: Surplus | Engineer
Description: Using a Relic refills 15% of Heavy Weapon Ammo. Bonus is doubled when Heavy Weapon is stowed. If the Stowed Heavy Weapon is overfilled, the Engineer will drop additional Ammo based on the surplus.

Name: Swift Shot | Gunslinger
Description: Gain 15% Fire Rate, 25% Ranged Damage and 5% Crit Chance for all firearms.

Name: Teamwork | Handler
Description: Handler and Companion gain 30% increased Revive Speed. While Handler or Companion are reviving, they receive 50% less damage.

Name: Reprocessed Heart
Description: On use, converts 5 Health as Grey Health to 40 Mod Power per second for 25s for both weapons. Cannot die from conversion.

Name: Urgency | Hunter
Description: Firearms gain 15% Reload Speed and 15% Increased Movement Speed after a Kill. Lasts 5s.

Name: Blooming Heart
Description: On use, heals the user for 35% of caster's Max Health over 5s. Spawns 3 Healing Orbs which grant 35% of caster's Max Health over 5s. Orbs last 20s. Recasting removes previous Orbs.

Name: Constrained Heart
Description: On use, regenerates 20 Health per second for 5s and grants 2 Stacks of BULWARK while heal is active.

Name: Crystal Heart
Description: On use, regenerates 100% of Max Health over 10s. Movement Speed is reduced by 50% and damage incoming is reduced by 25%. Lasts 10s.

Name: Decayed Heart
Description: On use, causes the next 3 instances of enemy damage taken to trigger 40 Health regeneration over 3s. Lasts 30s.

Name: Diverted Heart
Description: Does not provide standard healing. On use, reduces Skill Cooldowns by 1s per second. Lasts 15s.

Name: Dragon Heart
Description: On use, Heals 70 Health over 0.5s.

Name: Enlarged Heart
Description: Innate Double Use Speed. One use, heals 140 Health over 0.5s. Relic capacity is halved.

Name: Lifeless Heart
Description: On use, heals 30 Health over 0.5s. Relic capacity is doubled.

Name: Pulsing Heart
Description: On use, pulses every 3s, healing allies within 7m for 23 Health over 0.5s per pulse. Lasts 15s.

Name: Quilted Heart
Description: Does not provide standard healing. On use, negates Stamina Drain and cause Evades to heal for 15 Health over 0.25s. Lasts 20s.

Name: Runed Heart
Description: On use, increases Health Regeneration by 5 and generates 500 Mod Power over 10s for both weapons.

Name: Resonating Heart
Description: On use, regenerates 50% of Max Health over 5s. When heal ends, any overhealed Health is Doubled and awarded over the next 20s.

Name: Ripened Heart
Description: On.use, heals 35 Health over 0.5s and an additional 70 over 5s.

Name: Casting Speed
Description: Increases casting speed of Mods and Skills (Max +20%)

Name: Shielded Heart
Description: On use, grants a SHIELD for 100% of Max Health. Lasts 20s or until SHIELD is removed by damage.

Name: Siphon Heart
Description: On use, grants 10% of base damage dealt as Lifesteal for 10s.

Name: Tormented Heart
Description: Innate 20% Use Speed bonus. On use, deals 240 Explosive damage to enemies within 10m and Lifesteals 25% of damage dealt.

Name: Tranquil Heart
Description: Passively grants 2 Health Regeneration per second. On use, doubles All Health Regeneration for 15s.

Name: Unsullied Heart
Description: On use, heals for 100% of Current Health over 0.5s.

Name: Void Heart
Description: On use, reduces incoming damage by 50% for 4s. When buff ends, heals 100% of missing Health over 0.75s.

Name: Ammo Pickups
Description: Increases Ammo from Ammo drops (Max +30%)

Name: Ammo Reserves
Description: Increases Ammo Reserve capacity (Max +20%)

Name: Armor Effectiveness
Description: Increases damage resistance from Armor (Max +15%)

Name: Blight Resistance
Description: Increases Blight resistance (Max +30%)

Name: Mod Cost
Description: Decreases cost of executing mods (Max -10%)

Name: Charge Melee Cost
Description: Decreases stamina cost for charged melee attacks (Max -30%)

Name: Consumable Duration
Description: Increases effect duration of consumables (Max +20%)

Name: Consumable Speed
Description: Increases the speed of applying consumables (Max +15%)

Name: Damage Reduction
Description: Increases damage reduction (Max +5%)

Name: Elemental Damage
Description: Increases damage from elemental sources (Max +10%)

Name: Elemental Resistance
Description: Increases resistance to elemental damage (Max +10%)

Name: Health
Description: Increases maximum health (Max +15%)

Name: Melee Attack Speed
